			mix.orgtype.ig.ig        0.8673973  0.2712187      0 0.00143 ** 
			nodeifactor.orgtype.gov  0.9544805  0.1755724      0 < 1e-04 ***
			nodeofactor.orgtype.sci -0.0080528  0.2102326      0 0.96945    
			edgecov.committee       -0.0007542  0.0042259      0 0.85840    
			edgecov.nw.sci           3.3054513  0.6382601      0 < 1e-04 ***
			edgecov.infrep           1.0964583  0.1740745      0 < 1e-04 ***
			gwesp.fixed.0.1          2.2501767  1.0197470      0 0.02761 *  
